            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>iPhone 16e 將會正式發售，香港售價 HK$5,099 元對於不少用家來説是個心理關口，不論是 iPhone SE 還是 mini 系列的忠實用戶，看到這個價位可能都會稍為猶豫一下。但今次 iPhone 16e 比起以往的「經濟型」iPhone，卻在各方面——特別是智能電話最重要的核心元素——帶來了顯著提升。作為一名 iPhone 13 mini 的長期用家，這次有機會測試 iPhone 16e，讓我感受到它與舊機的明顯分別。以下是我認為值得留意的地方，特別是對像我這樣的 mini 系列粉絲來説，這部新機會否帶來驚喜。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294279" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05083-487x580.jpg" alt="" width="487" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05083-487x580.jpg 487w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05083.jpg 573w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 487px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294295" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05082-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05082-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05082.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>評測影片 :</h2><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_50889"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/9iRCqE910EM?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><h2></h2><br /><b>
